					<div class="spacer-s"></div>
					<p>We'll guide you in building a strong, Agile-centered product design practice, efficient design systems, and team-wide processes.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="item-block">
					<img src={MagnifyingGlassIcon.src} loading="lazy" alt="" class="item-image" />
					<h4>Evaluate your app's UX</h4>
					<div class="spacer-s"></div>
					<p>Our team of SaaS & enterprise usability specialists will conduct a UX design audit to highlight and prioritize areas for improvement.</p>
				</div>
