		<div class="content-container">
			<div class="case-study-section">
				<div class="case-study-image">
					<img src={TourialScreenshots.src} loading="lazy" alt="" class="constrained-full-image" />
				</div>
				<div class="case-study-content">
					<h2>Tourial</h2>
					<div class="spacer-m"></div>
					<p>Trailmerge crafted a scalable design system and designed new features in partnership with this Atlanta-based startup team focused on improving the SaaS sales process.</p>
					<div class="spacer-m"></div>
					<a href="#" class="button">Read More</a>
