		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Second Testimonial -->
	<div class="body-block quote-block">
		<div class="content-container">
			<div class="quote-wrapper">
				<img src={AndyHeadshot.src} loading="lazy" alt="" class="quote-image" />
				<div class="quote-text-wrapper">
					<blockquote>"Trailmerge is able to interpret a lot of scattered information around our design and UX goals and piece it together in a way that makes sense."</blockquote>
					<div class="spacer-s"></div>
