					<div class="spacer-s"></div>
					<div class="blog-feed-details">
						<div class="blog-feed-text">Mark Tegtmeier</div>
						<div class="divider"></div>
						<div class="blog-feed-text">Jul 8, 2022</div>
					</div>
					<div class="spacer-xs"></div>
					<a href="#" class="text-link">See Blog Post</a>
				</div>
				<div class="blog-feed-post-wrapper">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?w=400&h=200&fit=crop" loading="lazy" alt="Coffee and planning" class="blog-feed-image" />
					<div class="spacer-m"></div>
					<h4>How Do I Prioritize Features? Part 2 of 2</h4>
					<div class="spacer-s"></div>
					<div class="blog-feed-details">
						<div class="blog-feed-text">Mark Tegtmeier</div>
						<div class="divider"></div>
						<div class="blog-feed-text">Jun 9, 2021</div>
					</div>
					<div class="spacer-xs"></div>
